FORMAT: 1A
HOST: /

# Product Management API
A simple API for managing products

## Group Products
Product operations

### Products Collection [/api/products]

#### Get all products [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (array[Product])

#### Create a new product [POST]
+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (ProductInput)
+ Response 201 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Product)

### Product [/api/products/{product_id}]
+ Parameters
    + product_id: 1 (number, required) - Product ID

#### Get a product by ID [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Product)

#### Update a product [PUT]
+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (ProductInput)
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Product)

#### Delete a product [DELETE]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

## Data Structures

### ProductInput
+ name: `Awesome Product` (string, required) - Product name
+ price: 99.99 (number, required) - Product price
+ description: `A very awesome product` (string, optional) - Product description

### Product
+ id: 1 (number, required) - Product ID
+ name: `Awesome Product` (string, required) - Product name
+ price: 99.99 (number, required) - Product price
+ description: `A very awesome product` (string, optional) - Product description
